o 卡片 --> <div style=\"text-align: center; width: 280px; height: 120px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #333;\">Folo</p> <a href=\"https://app.follow.is/share/feeds/57360050739377168\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;\"> <img src=\"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.follow.is%2Ffeeds%3Fid%3D57360050739377168&query=%24.data.subscriptionCount&suffix=%20subs&logo=rss&label=Folo&color=ff5c00\" alt=\"Folo Subscription Count\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\"> </a> </div> <!-- NPM 卡片 --> <div style=\"text-align: center; width: 280px; height: 120px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #333;\">NPM</p> <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/~wuanqin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;\"> <img src=\"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.uuanqin.top%2Fnpm_stat_author_total.json&query=%24.total&suffix=%2Ftotal&label=downloads&color=cb3837&logo=npm\" alt=\"NPM Downloads\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\"> </a> </div> <!-- Greasy Fork 卡片 --> <div style=\"text-align: center; width: 280px; height: 120px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #333;\">Greasy Fork</p> <a href=\"https://greasyfork.org/zh-CN/scripts/466046-%E7%9F%A5%E7%BD%91-%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE-bibtex-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;\"> <img src=\"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://img.shields.io/greasyfork/dt/466046?label=bibtex%20TJU&logo=greasyfork&color=670000\" alt=\"Greasy Fork Downloads\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\"> </a> </div> <!-- OnlyFans 卡片 --> <div style=\"text-align: center; width: 280px; height: 120px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #333;\">OnlyFans</p> <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1TE411h7vY/?p=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;\"> <img src=\"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/subscribed%20-%20114514%20-%20?color=00aff0\" alt=\"OnlyFans Subscribed\" style=\"border: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\"> </a> </div> </div>\n<h1 id=\"本站简介\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#本站简介\"></a> 本站简介</h1>\n<p>为啥叫「半方池水半方田」？<s>有蓝有绿夺好…</s> 其实就是随意起的。实在要说意思那就是「一方天地」的意思。</p>\n<h2 id=\"️-小站历史\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#️-小站历史\"></a> 🗞️ 小站历史</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>2022\n<ul>\n<li>💻 拥有第一台服务器、域名，完成 ICP、公安联网备案，使用 Wordpress 建站。</li>\n<li>👍 灰度 (zhuang bi) 测试：假装不经意间向身边同学推荐文章，反响好评。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>2023\n<ul>\n<li>🗿 改用 Hexo 静态博客建站。</li>\n<li>👯 第一个主动添加本站的友链 @萌傀儡。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>2024\n<ul>\n<li>🚫 被某某办的蜀黍下架的技术性文章 1 篇；被藤迅 pp 墙。</li>\n<li>⭐ 公开发表了 100 篇博客文章。</li>\n<li>😈 首次经历 CDN 刷量攻击潮，遭遇 5+ 轮恶意刷量和非法检测；小破站被他人镜像。</li>\n<li>🔢 <a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"百味人生 / 我的空间\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202501010405800.webp\" data-desc=\"玩域名的大佬们点进来，博主在线卑微求助\" href='/p/fe5764d9/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>2024 年度数字</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>2025\n<ul>\n<li>🚫 被阿里云查水表。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>2026\n<ul>\n<li>TBD…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"️-技术信息\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#️-技术信息\"></a> 🛠️ 技术信息</h2>\n<p>注：点击超链接将跳转至本站相关的<strong>教程/笔记</strong>。<s>其实并不一定相关哈，反正目的在于引流…</s></p>\n<ul>\n<li>☁️ 服务商：阿里云（<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"百味人生 / 社会生活\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/pexels-pixabay-270700.jpg\" data-desc=\"个人博客网站建站的全流程以及要点提醒，以ECS阿里云服务器申请为例。\" href='/p/8be29a28/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>ECS、域名</a>）、腾讯云（<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/tencentcdn545.jpg\" data-desc=\"本文提供两类博客刷新边缘结点缓存的方法\" href='/p/b05ac1ee/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>CDN</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202508311854729.webp\" data-desc=\"保姆级指导对象存储云产品的使用\" href='/p/44a073f8/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>COS</a>、DNS）、Cloudflare（CDN、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202412100327066.webp\" data-desc=\"要补课的站长请点进来\" href='/p/55893d1/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>DNS</a>）</li>\n<li>⚙️ 基础设施：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"技术学习\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/git-flowcover555555.png\" data-desc=\"这是一篇对分支管理策略学习和探讨\" href='/p/6eb2089c/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>GitHub</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"工程\" data-auth=\"false\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202604211550776.webp\" data-desc=\"Vercel 应用实践记录集\" href='/p/11ce9d57/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Vercel</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEcover.png\" data-desc=\"精解域名配置，建议熟悉 CDN、HTTPS 配置后参考。\" href='/p/83335cfa/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Nginx</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/SSL_certificate-1cover.webp\" data-desc=\"SSL证书的不同部署方式以及CDN配置HTTPS。\" href='/p/6f54b93a/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Linux</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"计算机语言\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202409050037631.webp\" data-desc=\"SQL 刷题热身练习\" href='/p/12bc4bc9/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>MySQL</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"百味人生 / 数字与代码\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/RTFM_header_2cover.webp\" data-desc=\"有文档了也看不懂\" href='/p/ca685d6c/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>NPM</a>、PostgreSQL</li>\n<li>🔷 博客核心：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/hexobutifycover.webp\" data-desc=\"部署完 Hexo，选择一个好的主题进行更加个性化的定制。\" href='/p/18bbd410/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Hexo 框架</a> + <a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/butterflybeautifycover.webp\" data-desc=\"既然选择了 Butterfly 主题，那就好好装点一下吧\" href='/p/4872f379/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Butterfly 主题</a> + <a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Waline\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/diy-waline.png\" data-desc=\"通过修改客户端或服务端的配置定制自己的 Waline 评论区\" href='/p/dd188b35/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Waline 评论系统</a> + <a href=\"https://github.com/willow-god/Friend-Circle-Lite\">@willow-god Friend-Circle-Lite</a></li>\n<li>👨‍🌾 站长工具：百度站长、Webmasters、Google Search Console</li>\n<li>🧮 站点监控：Clarity、百度统计、Instatus、UptimeRobot</li>\n<li>🖇️ 自动化：GitHub Action、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/hexowordpresscover546546.png\" data-desc=\"将博客框架Hexo部署到ECS服务器。\" href='/p/ad28b4a/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Node.js</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同 / 自动化\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/githubstarcover.webp\" data-desc=\"介绍一些简单定时脚本的编写并利用 Webhook 推送\" href='/p/b9dad4e7/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Cron</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同 / 自动化\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/20240418211821.webp\" data-desc=\"舍友用了都说好\" href='/p/34fc0316/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>@Mrs4s go-cqhttp</a>、<a href=\"https://github.com/songquanpeng/message-pusher\">@songquanpeng message-pusher</a></li>\n<li>✒️ 写作工具：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"阿-测试文章\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/mdcover65465.png\" data-desc=\"以 CommonMark、GFM 标准为基础进行测试。\" href='/p/3c4a82e6/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Markdown</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/hexoobsidian-Grammar.webp\" data-desc=\"本文介绍了使用插件使得 Hexo 接受部分 OFM 语法的方法\" href='/p/d4bc55f2/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Markdown-it</a>、Mermaid、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/hexoobsidian-cowork.webp\" data-desc=\"切换到 Obsidian 写作的快速指南\" href='/p/51890a9/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Obsidian</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同 / 自动化\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202412092107480.webp\" data-desc=\"保姆级解释PicGo配置腾讯云的步骤。\" href='/p/edfe8057/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>PicGo</a>、WebStorm</li>\n<li>🤖 AI 能力：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"工程\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202602240313353.webp\" data-desc=\"RAG 环节中的向量数据库的创建与使用\" href='/p/f3908a2e/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Spring AI</a>、阿里云百炼、DeepSeek、Hunyuan-lite、<a href=\"https://github.com/willow-god/hexo-ai-summary\">@willow-god hexo-ai-summary</a></li>\n<li>🪞 静态资源：Unpkg、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/jsdeliver-banned.png\" data-desc=\"本文介绍 Butterfly 下替换 CDN 链接的解决方案\" href='/p/7b17333d/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>国内镜像站</a>（饿了么、南方科技大学）</li>\n<li>🔶 其他服务：Algolia、RSS、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Waline\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/diy-waline.png\" data-desc=\"为网站建立邮件服务\" href='/p/81d7e338/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>腾讯企业邮</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Waline\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202410130307005.webp\" data-desc=\"简要介绍常用公共头像服务，尝试在 Waline 中上手实践替换默认头像\" href='/p/1d248fa3/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Cravatar</a>、Follow、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / Hexo\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202604090356813.webp\" data-desc=\"AI Coding的一次实践，为授权文章功能做基础\" href='/p/131c2726/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Keycloak</a>、D3.js</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🗑️ 已弃用的工具和服务：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"博客站点维护 / WordPress\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/WPPIC.png\" data-desc=\"简要介绍ECS中Wordpress的搭建\" href='/p/377ca42c/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>WordPress</a>、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" data-cate=\"核心协同\" data-cover=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202409050034102.webp\" data-desc=\"介绍继续使用 Typora 免费版或正式版的方法\" href='/p/43ae38fe/'><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>Typora</a>、LeanCloud、<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_bla